codex
`TextureRenderer` uses `Graphics::setRenderTarget(destinationTexture, ...)` but does not allocate a 
screen-sized target; on gl11, ordinary destination textures route through the plugin’s fixed 512x512 
bake target. I’m opening that path for the final notes because it is one of the candidates you named.
